message:
Yesterday we had the pleasure of meeting with Young & Hungry a Creative Co-Op's creative director, Jim Wojtowicz and Vendela Ängek, student and project lead on our collaboration.  I had the opportunity to see the work the students have been dedicating their time to this semester. 
We are very lucky to work with this amazing, intelligent, creative and passionate group of students. We can't wait for everyone to see the projects they've  created to help educate parents and children about child trafficking. 
#inspired 
#creatingchange
